<template>

        class="text-capitalize gst-search-all-btn"
        color="primary"
        v-bind="$attrs"
        @click="$emit('click')">
        {{ $t('shared:components.buttons.seeAll') }}

        name: 'SeeAllButton',

        border-radius: border-radius( 'm' ) !important;

        &.v-btn--disabled {

    .gst-search-all-btn.v-btn.v-btn--outlined:not([disabled]) {
